text: Phrynetopsis thomensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Karl Jordan in 1903. It is known from São Tomé and Príncipe.BioLib.cz - Phrynetopsis thomensis. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1903
